  "title": "query result is wrong when IndexLookUp PushDown with partition table",
  "description": "## Bug Report\n\nPlease answer these questions before submitting your issue. Thanks!\n\n### 1. Minimal reproduce step (Required)\n\n```sql\ncreate table t3 (id int, a int, b int, c int, primary key(id), index idx(b)) partition by hash (id) partitions 3;\ninsert into t3 values (1,1,1,1), (2,2,2,2);\nselect /*+ index_lookup_pushdown(t3, idx)*/ * from t3 use index(idx) where b>=0 and b<=10;\n```\n\n<!-- a step by step guide for reproducing the bug. -->\n\n### 2. What did you expect to see? (Required)\n\n```sql\ntest> select /*+ index_lookup_pushdown(t3, idx)*/ * from t3 use index(idx) where b>=0 and b<=10;\n+----+---+---+---+\n| id | a | b | c |\n+----+---+---+---+\n| 1  | 1 | 1 | 1 |\n| 2  | 2 | 2 | 2 |\n+----+---+---+---+\n```\n\n### 3. What did you see instead (Required)\n\n```sql\ntest> select /*+ index_lookup_pushdown(t3, idx)*/ * from t3 use index(idx) where b>=0 and b<=10;\n+----+---+---+---+\n| id | a | b | c |\n+----+---+---+---+\n+----+---+---+---+\n0 rows in set\n```\n\n### 4. What is your TiDB version? (Required)\n\n<!-- Paste the output of SELECT tidb_version() -->\n\n```sql\ntest> select tidb_version();\n+-----------------------------------------------------------+\n| tidb_version()                                            |\n+-----------------------------------------------------------+\n| Release Version: v9.0.0-beta.2.pre-779-ge10a603ea1        |\n| Edition: Community                                        |\n| Git Commit Hash: e10a603ea1bd0865b2b6b3f55066c5ddc68986e9 |\n| Git Branch: HEAD                                          |\n| UTC Build Time: 2025-11-15 10:41:44                       |\n| GoVersion: go1.23.12                                      |\n| Race Enabled: false                                       |\n| Check Table Before Drop: false                            |\n| Store: tikv                                               |\n| Kernel Type: Classic                                      |\n+-----------------------------